SUMMARY:Review & update batch API documentation for session discoverability
DESCRIPTION:Review and update documentation for the ADR-008 Batch API feature to ensure future Claude sessions can discover the architecture quickly.\n\nFiles to review/update:\n- docs/backend/operational-state.md — current extraction mode per domain\n- docs/architecture/convergence-narrative.md — add batch API outcome\n- CLAUDE.md — verify batch API workflow is described in Developer Workflow section\n- docs/backend/workflow-guide.md — update Mode A steps for submit/collect flow\n- docs/backend/daily-run-log.md — add batch_pending as a valid pipeline state\n\nKey things to document:\n- submit_batch.py → collect_batch.py day-boundary handoff\n- EXIT_PENDING (rc=2) behavior in run_pipeline.py\n- batch_jobs table schema and status lifecycle\n- make submit / make collect / make post-collect targets
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
